quadtree.contentMinimized: 2D Physics, er eit kollisjonssystem som bruker Quadtree for å auke ytelsen på 2D kollisjon.

quadtree.contentMinimized: 2D Physics, is a collision system  that uses a Quadtree to increase performance for 2D collisions.
quadtree.contentMaximized: Quadtree is a data structure that divides a coordinate system, in our case the screenspace into 4 quadrants and thereafter is used to check if elements within each quadrant and their positions overlap and then adjust the positions when that is the case.
